{"tid":1415344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上兵伐謀;其次伐交;其永伐兵;其下伐城","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T02:04:40.000Z","uid":257398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"205d3dbda97c295a4ffe3d08f4979eca82551c1a","tid":1415344,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"故兵無常勢，水無常形<br />\n能因敵變化而取勝者，謂之神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足們要記得我地當初點解企出嚟<br />\n<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選"},{"pid":"7cd0351b07998121fadff4cb05d7e03ab55fa3b7","tid":1415344,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求</span>"},{"pid":"19d469eced60f037c99a5969a25d943dd775f4b5","tid":1415344,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></span>"},{"pid":"be17531e43c066f93dd96d65a4ce1a03d0fa13c2","tid":1415344,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:36:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></span>"},{"pid":"07eb44829ec42165d0b94f469a1d0109959ac56c","tid":1415344,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></span>"},{"pid":"89859ae1c9cd5463f331d3769f8d8aebd09b5a39","tid":1415344,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></span>"},{"pid":"d80bce2d42c356a1cececc27f320cc9b21703781","tid":1415344,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"孫子所講既 <span sty